210
00:13:11,870 --> 00:13:12,870
It's fine.

211
00:13:12,910 --> 00:13:14,620
You have security

212
00:13:14,700 --> 00:13:16,330
and first aid on-site, right?

213
00:13:16,620 --> 00:13:19,370
I'll be okay.

214
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,540
I still wouldn't

215
00:13:21,620 --> 00:13:24,250
