216
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:28,200
Alright, I'll get ready.

217
00:13:28,330 --> 00:13:29,540
It's fine, really.

218
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:57,660
Chu has low blood sugar?

219
00:13:58,500 --> 00:14:00,080
She's going to the hot springs alone?

220
00:14:22,870 --> 00:14:23,790
We don't know

221
00:14:23,910 --> 00:14:25,330
where Lanshan and Shwenny

222
00:14:25,660 --> 00:14:26,700
