223
00:14:26,950 --> 00:14:27,950
You have no idea.

224
00:14:28,330 --> 00:14:29,040
Only someone

225
00:14:29,160 --> 00:14:31,000
as charming and brilliant as me,

226
00:14:31,160 --> 00:14:33,290
with the best instincts around,
could figure that out.

227
00:14:41,660 --> 00:14:42,370
Excuse me,

228
00:14:42,500 --> 00:14:43,370
could you check the room numbers

229
00:14:43,500 --> 00:14:45,200
for Sheng Shi and Gu Lanshan?

230
00:14:45,410 --> 00:14:46,410
Sorry, sir,

231
00:14:46,500 --> 00:14:48,580
we can't disclose guest information.

232
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:51,580
I'll give you another chance.

233
00:14:51,910 --> 00:14:52,580
Mr. Ji.

234
00:14:52,660 --> 00:14:53,370
Even if you're Mr. Ji,

235
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:55,370
we can't break the rules.

236
00:14:55,500 --> 00:14:56,540
It's against the law.

237
00:14:56,660 --> 00:14:57,700
I'm just asking for a room number.

238
00:14:57,750 --> 00:14:58,450
How hard can it be?

239
00:14:58,500 --> 00:14:59,120
Let's go

240
00:14:59,620 --> 00:15:00,830
