249
00:15:21,040 --> 00:15:22,040
Even if he did, it's no big deal.

250
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:23,580
Don't worry about it.

251
00:15:23,660 --> 00:15:25,160
That's good.

252
00:15:25,330 --> 00:15:26,950
I'll be on my way then.

253
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:28,120
Goodbye, Uncle Ji.

254
00:15:28,410 --> 00:15:29,370
Goodbye.

255
00:15:37,660 --> 00:15:38,700
