266
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:19,790
Take him!

267
00:16:20,500 --> 00:16:21,290
No, wait!

268
00:16:21,660 --> 00:16:24,330
Fanhua, help me!

269
00:16:29,500 --> 00:16:32,500
Mr. Lu, weren't we here
to talk business?

270
00:16:33,040 --> 00:16:36,330
Isn't this us talking business?

271
00:16:42,160 --> 00:16:43,200
Lu Yifan.

272
00:16:46,870 --> 00:16:47,870
Here you are.

273
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:50,950
Lu Yifan, it's one thing to fool around,

274
00:16:51,410 --> 00:16:52,910
