276
00:16:55,870 --> 00:16:56,870
Gu En,

277
00:16:57,580 --> 00:16:58,700
marrying you

278
00:16:59,160 --> 00:17:01,040
was already a charity on my part.

279
00:17:03,700 --> 00:17:04,830
